column2: SELECT up_id, (SELECT apstar_id FROM fGetNearestApogeeStarEq(up_ra,up_dec,#)) as apstar_id   FROM #upload WHERE (SELECT apstar_id FROM fGetNearestApogeeStarEq(up_ra,up_dec,#)) IS NOT NULL  SELECT u.up_SourceId as [SourceId], s.* FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN apogeestar s ON s.apstar_id = x.apstar_id
